eNCA’s Lethiwe Mdluli reports. Courtesy #DStv403  DURBAN - Cracking walls, no running water and no electricity. These are some of the problems beneficiaries of a multimillion-rand housing project have to deal with in Tongaat, north of Durban. The residents say they are resorting to illegal electricity connections. eNCA’s Lethiwe Mdluli has the details in the video above.